<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>SmartZone-Mobilephone Store</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/x-icon"
      href="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/89/f1/d6/89f1d65fe8b8bf81eb8ddbb417537d17.jpg"
    />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <meta content="" name="keywords" />
    <meta content="" name="description" />
    <!-- Google Web Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <!-- Glide.js CSS -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@glidejs/glide@3.6.0/dist/css/glide.core.min.css"
    />

    <!-- Glide.js JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@glidejs/glide@3.6.0/dist/glide.min.js"></script>

    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Raleway:wght@600;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <!-- Icon Font Stylesheet -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- Libraries Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/lib/lightbox/css/lightbox.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
      href="/client/lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.carousel.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- Customized Bootstrap Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!-- Template Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="/client/css/support/return.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="/client/css/layout/layout.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Spinner Start -->
    <div
      id="spinner"
      class="show d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
    >
      <div class="spinner-border text-primary" role="status"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- header -->
    <%- include('../layout/header') %>
    <!-- banner -->
    <%- include('../layout/banner') %>
    <div class="container py-5">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/" class="fw-bold">Home</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">
            30 Day Return
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <hr />
    </div>
    <div class="container py-4">
      <div class="section-box">
        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4 text-center">Return Policy</h2>
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <h5 class="return-section-title">1. Return conditions</h5>
        <p>
          Customers are required to check the condition of the goods and may
          return or exchange them at the time of delivery/receipt in the
          following cases:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-x-circle-fill"></i>
            The goods are not of the correct type or model as specified in the
            placed order or as displayed on the website at the time of ordering.
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-box-seam"></i>
            The quantity is insufficient or the set is incomplete as per the
            order.
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill text-warning"></i>
            The external condition is affected, such as torn packaging, peeling,
            or damage.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Customers are responsible for presenting relevant documents to prove
          the aforementioned issues to complete the return or exchange process.
        </p>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <h5 class="return-section-title">
          2. Regulations on the time of notification and sending products to
          return
        </h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i>
            Duration of return and exchange: Within 72 hours from the time of
            receiving the product in cases of missing accessories, gifts, or
            damaged goods.
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-calendar-check-fill"></i>
            Product transfer time: Within 15 days from the time of receiving the
            product.
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-danger"></i>
            Product return location: Customers can bring the goods directly to
            our office/store or send them via postal service.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3">
          In case customers have feedback or complaints regarding product
          quality, please contact our customer service hotline.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer  -->
    <%- include('../layout/footer') %>
    <a href="#" class="btn border-3 rounded-circle back-to-top"
      ><i class="fa fa-arrow-up"></i
    ></a>
    <!--  -->
    <script
      src="//code.tidio.co/jessuvetqgbmlfbbicxo08yqsjeeprfb.js"
      async
    ></script>

    <!-- JavaScript Libraries -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/client/lib/easing/easing.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/client/lib/waypoints/waypoints.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/client/lib/lightbox/js/lightbox.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/client/lib/owlcarousel/owl.carousel.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Template Javascript -->
    <script src="/client/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
